User Agent Entropy

A Chrome Extension that adds entropy to your User Agent headers.

To install,

 1. Clone this repo
 2. Open chrome://chrome/extensions/
 3. Select "Load unpacked extension..."
 4. Select the directory you created in Step 1

To test,

 1. Go to http://panopticlick.eff.org/index.php
 2. Select "Test Me"
 3. Reload a few times
 4. Observe that your User Agent changes on each request
